translations: v．闲逛，漫步：指在无目的、悠闲地行走或闲逛。
· He swanned around the party, chatting with everyone.
他在聚会上闲逛，和每个人聊天。

phrs.translation: 绝笔，最后的作品；天鹅临死时的叫声

sentences.sentence: I recently swanned through immigration both ways in seconds and was only slightly disappointed to see that on neither occasion was there any line in front of the usual booths.
sentences.translation: 我最近进出过这个地方，每次都只花费几秒钟的时间，而且我略感失望的发现常规过境服务台前已经没有长长的等待队伍了。
